A six-tile entry-point grid linking to all four ReceiptScanner
Special pages plus the two manual-entry forms. Drop it on any page
(the wiki's Main_Page is the natural home):

  {{Receipt dashboard}}

The tiles are:

* Upload receipt — Special:UploadReceipt
* New expense — Special:FormEdit/Expense (manual entry, no OCR)
* New income — Special:FormEdit/Income (manual entry, no OCR)
* Review — Special:ReceiptReview (triage parsed entries)
* Ledger — Special:Ledger (filter / total / CSV)
* Unlinked files — Special:UnlinkedFiles (uploaded files not yet entered)

The {{#receiptscanner_dashboard:}} parser function below renders the
markup; styling comes from [[Template:Receipt dashboard/styles.css]]
via TemplateStyles.
